 Quest VR headset.\n\u2022 Follow and Engage: Connect with friends and creators, follow their spatial video journeys, and never miss a moment in 3D.\n\nJoin Sotial today \u2013 where your world leaps into the new dimension of social media!\n\nNotes:\n\u2022 Capturing spatial videos requires an iPhone 15 Pro/Max or newer.", "short_description": "Share and Experience the World in a New Dimension!\n\nSotial is a pioneering social media service that brings spatial video to your fingertips. From the everyday to the extraordinary, Sotial transforms your world into a captivating immersive experience."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://about.amazevr.com/privacy-notice", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.amazevr.com/termsofservice", "publisher_name": "AmazeVR", "support_website_url": "https://amazevr.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/", "website_url": "https://www.sotial.io/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "434961926215971"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7211517985577446"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031425_931506138484211_2492515146861246284_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Leg-wOorctAQ7kNvgEBBy0j&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBLe8klDYmF-Igl2EopyF88M-PcmG5QCTL5l1c8oAozog&oe=6772793C"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": fal